---
title: Sweet Miso Chicken & Sesame Fries with Japanese Pear Salad
description: Miso, the umami-rich classic Japanese ingredient, gets a starring role in this marinade, where it adds a tasty touch to seared chicken. Add some golden sesame-coated fries on the side plus a fresh green salad loaded with a Japanese dressing, and we've transformed a classic dinner formula into a flavoursome feast!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-miso-chicken-sesame-fries-aa1d3f52.jpg
